- Jangan di sini.
- Kenapa?

808
01:17:05,833 --> 01:17:07,291
Kumohon. Kami lelah.

809
01:17:07,375 --> 01:17:10,250
- Dia wanita. Kami butuh tempat.
- Bukan urusanku.

810
01:17:14,083 --> 01:17:15,000
Maaf, sudah penuh.

811
01:17:15,083 --> 01:17:17,416
Ya. Aku tahu. Tapi bisakah kau...

812
01:17:17,500 --> 01:17:19,875
Bisa jelaskan apa yang sedang terjadi?

813
01:17:19,958 --> 01:17:22,125
Seorang Anak akan lahir di Betlehem.

814
01:17:22,625 --> 01:17:23,708
Anak apa?

815
01:17:23,791 --> 01:17:24,708
Sang Mesias.

816
01:17:40,958 --> 01:17:41,875
Nak,

817
01:17:42,916 --> 01:17:43,958
