841
01:20:09,541 --> 01:20:10,666
Sudah waktunya.

842
01:20:16,041 --> 01:20:16,916
Ayo.

843
01:20:18,666 --> 01:20:19,541
Ibu bersamamu.

844
01:20:36,083 --> 01:20:37,250
